      "outputs": [
        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"usage\">Usage</h1>\n<h2 id=\"basic-usage\">Basic Usage</h2>\n<h4 id=\"a-simple-configuration\">A simple configuration</h4>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">We will demonstrate basic usage of <code>config-foundry</code> using a simple configuration containing a <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YAML\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">YAML</a> file called <code>config.yml</code> and a <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comma-separated_values\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">CSV</a> file called <code>data.csv</code>.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">A concrete instance of this configuration already exists in the <code>./basic</code> directory.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
    {
      "id": "vblA",
      "code_hash": "2d3b139ec1a7af63a1499a3f9704ce39",
      "outputs": [
