            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h3 id=\"subclassing-metaconfig\">Subclassing <code>MetaConfig</code></h3>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">The next step is to specify a valid configuration in terms of its files and handlers.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">To do this we will use the <code>make_metaconfig</code> function, which produces a subclass of <code>MetaConfig</code> whose fields correspond to the two required files.</span></span>"
