            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h4 id=\"writing-configurations\">Writing configurations</h4>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">In-memory configurations can be written to the filesystem using the <code>write</code> method.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">For the purpose of illustration we will modify the configuration and then write it to a temporary directory.</span></span>"
