            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h3 id=\"variable-paths\">Variable paths</h3>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Often configurations are flexible regarding paths and file names.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Here we do not fix the file name for <code>data</code> - perhaps it differs between configurations (e.g. based on a path set in <code>config.yml</code>).</span></span>"
