            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\"><code>UnspecifiedPathHandler</code> now requires the <strong>relative</strong> path corresponding to <code>data</code> to be provided upon instantiation.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">!!! note\n    Under the hood, the provided path is transformed into a <code>Node</code> in the <code>__post_init__</code> dataclass method.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
