            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h4 id=\"handler-inference\">Handler inference</h4>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">More usefully, we leave the handler to be inferred by the file extension.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">We first load the original 'basic' configuration.</span></span>"
