          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\">We see that <code>DummyHandler.read</code> was never called, and instead we are shown a warning that <code>read('optional.file')</code> was filtered out by a test (which we are shown the code for). Note that this warning can be disabled by setting <code>warn=False</code> (the default) in <code>filter_missing</code>.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">The configuration <code>dict</code> contains an entry corresponding to the <code>optional</code> node, but it has a special <em>sentinel</em> value, <code>MISSING</code>.</span></span>"
